data.text:
If you follow me on Instagram, you’ve probably have noticed how much I’ve been wearing WAYF lately. I’ve always been a huge fan of the brand because of their modern, feminine and chic approach to women’s fashion.

If you are currently looking to give yourself a little wardrobe refresh, I highly recommend you stop by here and here to discover more styles! I’m currently crushing on this matching set! How adorable is the color? It’s so chic and timeless, this is a color that will for remain relevant for a while!

Keep scrolling for more WAYF styles! I’ve rounded up a few of my favorite styles from different retailers!

Happy shopping my friends! Thanks so much for stopping by!

SHOP THE LOOK
